results.name: Index of appearance of 2*prime(n) in A336957, or -1 if 2*prime(n) never appears.
comment: It is a strong conjecture that 2*prime(n) appears in A336957 for all n>1, and it is known that 4 does not appear.
See also the comment in A336957 discussing when primes first appear in A336957.
